// Replace your existing form state handlers with these optimized versions // Owner form handlers const handleOwnerFormChange = (field, value) => { setOwnerForm(prev => ({ ...prev, [field]: value })); }; // Renter form handlers const handleRenterFormChange = (field, value) => { setRenterForm(prev => ({ ...prev, [field]: value })); }; // Updated OwnerScreen with fixed form handlers const OwnerScreen = () => (

Property Listing Submission

handleOwnerFormChange('name', e.target.value)} required placeholder=" " id="ownerName" />
handleOwnerFormChange('email', e.target.value)} required placeholder=" " id="ownerEmail" />
handleOwnerFormChange('location', e.target.value)} required placeholder=" " id="ownerLocation" />
handleOwnerFormChange('size', e.target.value)} required min="50" placeholder=" " id="ownerSize" />
handleOwnerFormChange('price', e.target.value)} required min="10" placeholder=" " id="ownerPrice" />
handleOwnerFormChange('image', e.target.files[0])} required /> Upload a clear, high-resolution photo of the space
); // Updated RenterScreen with fixed form handlers const RenterScreen = () => (

New Parking Booking

handleRenterFormChange('name', e.target.value)} required placeholder=" " id="renterName" />
handleRenterFormChange('email', e.target.value)} required placeholder=" " id="renterEmail" />
handleRenterFormChange('phone', e.target.value)} required placeholder=" " pattern="[0-9]{10}" id="renterPhone" />
handleRenterFormChange('image', e.target.files[0])} required /> Upload a photo of your vehicle.
handleRenterFormChange('date', e.target.value)} required min={new Date().toISOString().split('T')[0]} id="renterDate" />
handleRenterFormChange('startTime', e.target.value)} required id="renterStart" />
handleRenterFormChange('endTime', e.target.value)} required id="renterEnd" />
₹{calculatePrice()}
Rate: ₹50 per hour
);
